mjc.types

Class BuiltInType

  • java.lang.Object
    • mjc.types.Type
      • mjc.types.BuiltInType

  • public class BuiltInType
extends Type
    BuiltInType represents a built-in MiniJava type.

    There are only five static instances of this class, one for each of the built-in types int, int[], long, long[] and boolean.
